ToSay.value: Veigar: Your resistance bores me... fight to the death for my amusement!
Veigar: NO! Why do I keep relying on you incompetents!
Veigar: Ha ha! Now back to crushing your nexus!
Veigar: No! I will not be defeated! I am INVINCIBLE!
Veigar: Even death trembles in my presence!
Veigar: Your pathetic attempt at resistance is hopeless! Minions! Crush them for me!

spellData.desc: Blasts target enemy champion, dealing Magic Damage plus 25% of the target's maximum Mana. If Primordial Burst deals a killing blow, Ruby_Boss_FNVeigar regains Mana.
